data.revised_prompt: Imagine a landscape scene with alien soldiers dressed in armor reminiscent of futuristic paladin style. They are equipped with advanced weaponry technology. Each alien soldier has unique physical attributes which are a blend of varying terrestrial and extraterrestrial characteristics. The setting is an otherworldly landscape with robust flora and distinct geological features that one would imagine finding on a distant, unexplored planet. The lighting is ethereal, creating a distinct divide between the familiar and the alien elements in the scene. These soldiers, ready in their stance, signal their readiness to maintain order in their realm.
